  "texts": [
    "Overall, GPT-4 has the potential to significantly enhance patient care by providing clinicians with advanced decision support and real-time insights, improving diagnostic accuracy and treatment planning.",
    "However, its implementation also raises concerns about data privacy, as handling sensitive patient information requires stringent safeguards to prevent breaches.",
    "Currently, there is a global shortage of experienced pathologists.",
    "Excessive workload frequently leads to misdiagnoses in clinical practice.",
    "The diagnostic capabilities also vary significantly across medical institutions."
  ]
}